<subSubSection pageId="20" pageNumber="299" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="20.[973,1775,2708,3280]" pageId="20" pageNumber="299">
<taxonomicName authorityName="Aellen" authorityYear="1973" box="[975,1272,2869,2908]" class="Mammalia" family="Rhinolophidae" genus="Rhinolophus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="20" pageNumber="299" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="hilli">
<emphasis box="[975,1272,2869,2908]" italics="true" pageId="20" pageNumber="299">Rhinolophus hilli</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is in the 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Pousargues" authorityYear="1897" box="[1471,1627,2869,2908]" class="Mammalia" family="Rhinolophidae" genus="Rhinolophus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="20" pageNumber="299" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="maclaudi">
<emphasis box="[1471,1627,2869,2908]" italics="true" pageId="20" pageNumber="299">maclaudi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
species group and was considered a subspecies of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Pousargues" authorityYear="1897" box="[975,1186,2975,3014]" class="Mammalia" family="Rhinolophidae" genus="Rhinolophus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="20" pageNumber="299" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="maclaudi">
<emphasis box="[975,1186,2975,3014]" italics="true" pageId="20" pageNumber="299">R maclaudi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<emphasis box="[1281,1770,2975,3015]" italics="true" pageId="20" pageNumber="299">
subsequently 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Hill" authorityYear="1942" box="[1534,1764,2975,3015]" class="Mammalia" family="Rhinolophidae" genus="Rhinolophus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="20" pageNumber="299" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="ruwenzorii">R ruwenzorii</taxonomicName>
.
</emphasis>
Recent morphological studies support its recognition as a distinct species. 
<emphasis box="[1562,1762,3082,3121]" italics="true" pageId="20" pageNumber="299">Monotypic</emphasis>
.
</paragraph>
<caption ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3749980" ID-Zenodo-Dep="3749980" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3749980/files/figure.png" inLine="true" pageId="20" pageNumber="299" targetBox="[142,942,2711,3272]" targetPageId="20">
